Vol / Page:  6
Edition:
Quote:  He did, immediately after returning to town, write to me to be good enough to inform him when I mustered, so that he might be present, and claim any sheep not marked with the bottle-brand .. The bottle-brand was of pitch and tar, and would have been as visible as the station-brand.
